<div
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h1 style="color: #333; font-size: 20px;">Dear {{ username }},</h1>

    <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.5;">
        The following information on your account has been updated :
    </p>

    <ul style="color: #555; line-height: 1.5;">
        {{#if changes.emailChanged}}<li>Email</li>{{/if}}
        {{#if changes.usernameChanged}}<li>Username</li>{{/if}}
        {{#if changes.passwordChanged}}<li>Password</li>{{/if}}
    </ul>

    <p style="color: rgb(199, 75, 75); line-height: 1.5;">
        If you were not at the origin of these changes, please contact us.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-weight: bold; color: #333;">
        Have a great day !
    </p>
</div>